nodes.text: Star Wars: Doctor Aphra Book VII: Unspeakable Rebel Superweapon

Star Wars: Doctor Aphra Book VII: Unspeakable Rebel Superweapon is the seventh story arc of Marvel Comics' original Doctor Aphra comic-book series. The arc was written by Simon Spurrier with art by Wilton Santos, Caspar Wijngaard, Andrea Broccardo, and Cris Bolson.
